Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:05.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,41 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:10.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There was a man who created trouble in the Wano Country named Kozuki Oden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:13.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His followers came together,...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:18.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...and he stepped into the lawless land, Kuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.26,Main,,0,0,0,,You're Kozuki Oden, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:42.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been disavowed,\Nso I no longer have a name!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:47.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyone can enter,\Nbut those who try to leave will be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:49.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Especially samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:58.11,Main,,0,0,0,,It is so restrictive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:04.16,Main,,0,0,0,,How can anyone live in a place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:06.70,Main,,0,0,0,,That's hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:10.79,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll never be able to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:12.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, don't even try to get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:16.25,Main,,0,0,0,,"Don't even try to get out"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:19.92,Main,,0,0,0,,That's my least favorite rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:23.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I make rules in this area!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:24.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Cut him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:01.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you the boss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:19.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden... I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:22.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Try your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:26.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:28.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:32.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Look! The gate has been broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:44.51,Main,,0,0,0,,You fools who grew up pampered in the capital...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:48.35,Main,,0,0,0,,...can't understand what it\Nfeels like to live in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:52.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that what you wanna say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:59.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:03.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop barking in a small yard like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:33.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:35.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:52.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden-san! We're here to back you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:57.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:06:01.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I've just finished it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:05.80,Main,,0,0,0,,It took me a whole day, all through the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:17.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Kill me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:19.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I know what the future holds anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:22.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I have no regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:27.90,Main,,0,0,0,,He's the infamous Ashura Doji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:30.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:35.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you still love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:41.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Help me with your wisdom and strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:47.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I've decided to head up this helpless scum...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:51.14,Main,,0,0,0,,...as their king!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:05.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Shogun-sama! It's Oden-sama again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:09.07,Main,,0,0,0,,What? What did he do this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:11.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:20.21,Main,,0,0,0,,That lawless Kuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:23.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Only he could do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:26.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Is this all true?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:34.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Leading the roughnecks of Kuri,\Nthe bloody, hellish land,...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:42.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...Oden utilized their abundant energy\Nand turned the wild land into a habitable place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:54.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In reaction to this accomplishment,\NKozuki Sukiyaki, the Shogun, dropped his disavowal,...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.31,0:07:58.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...and gave his son the title\Nof the Daimyo of Kuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:02.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Our great Oden-sama\Nwill become the Daimyo of Kuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:03.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:06.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Then it'll become a full-fledged province!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:09.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it! But we stuck it out, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:15.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Kin-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:21.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Congratulations! Our precious Oden-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:22.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.75,Main,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Oden-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:25.23,Main,,0,0,0,,You finally became Kuri's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:26.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:32.15,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:40.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Daimyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:09:00.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden-sama! Oden-sama! Oden-sama! Oden-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:04.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden-sama! Oden-sama! Oden-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:14.61,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ashura?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:17.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:23.95,Main,,0,0,0,,...have never seen peace before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:28.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:31.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Don't creep me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:38.39,Main,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:41.43,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:42.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:45.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I said "Stop"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:47.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:49.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:50.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Knock it off already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:53.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, a Daimyo needs vassals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:10:00.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Rather than being assigned with\Nsome wise and sober men,...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:03.24,Main,,0,0,0,,...I want you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:16.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Be my samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:40.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:45.96,Main,,0,0,0,,S-S-Stop! You're snotting! It's coming out!\NOh, it's on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:48.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:52.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Then, six years later...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:55.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...33 years before the present day,...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:11:01.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...elsewhere across the world, the remnants of the disbanded legendary Rocks Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:07.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...each formed a new crew,\Nextended their influence, and became infamous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:20.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Are they animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:23.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Just hairy men?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:30.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Odd-shaped creatures?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:38.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:39.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:04.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Far back, several hundred years ago,...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:10.16,Main,,0,0,0,,...we Minks\Nand the Kozuki samurai of the Wano Country...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:14.02,Main,,0,0,0,,...made a pledge and became sworn allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:17.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn! The Wano Country is the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:20.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Get me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:23.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a kappa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:24.84,Main,,0,0,0,,So you're an imp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:27.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish we never set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:29.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish we didn't come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:32.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Screw that sworn ally crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:35.90,Main,,0,0,0,,A cat monster, dog monster, and a kappa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:39.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Is this beach cursed? Let's burn them alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:43.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:51.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I got enough ingredients for today's oden...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:01.46,Main,,0,0,0,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:13.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Shame on you, you pricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:16.98,Main,,0,0,0,,You fear those who aren't like you\Nbecause you're ignorant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:19.94,Main,,0,0,0,,How could you bully those little ones?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:23.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:27.78,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:29.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't leave us like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:39.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Who are those little creatures?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:40.63,Main,,0,0,0,,They followed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:45.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you for saving us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:48.84,Main,,0,0,0,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:53.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Sign of hunger and the shipwreck,\Nwe were almost killed by violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:57.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! This is too hot to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:14:02.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa... I can't get used to\Nseeing animals talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:08.45,Main,,0,0,0,,The Minks! My father once told me about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:12.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought so!\NWe have that symbol in our country, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:14.91,Main,,0,0,0,,You-gara people and us are brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:18.21,Main,,0,0,0,,And you saved our lives!\NWe were starving...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:20.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I see... Eat as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:22.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, savior!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:26.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be shy. You'll like radish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:28.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't forget this favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:30.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Have some hanpen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:32.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Konnyaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:34.89,Main,,0,0,0,,No! It's too hot to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:42.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I have a sensitive tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:44.57,Main,,0,0,0,,You evil cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:46.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait, Neko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:50.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Neko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:54.03,Main,,0,0,0,,If it didn't boil...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:56.62,Main,,0,0,0,,...it wouldn't be Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.79,Main,,0,0,0,,That's kind of cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:04.09,Main,,0,0,0,,To me, it's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:06.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:09.72,Main,,0,0,0,,The ship we were on sank\Nand my mother and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:13.26,Main,,0,0,0,,...were cast ashore in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:16.56,Main,,0,0,0,,We asked for help, but the people threw rocks at us\Nbecause we were Fish-Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:21.44,Main,,0,0,0,,My mother got hurt,\Nso we couldn't go back to where we came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:23.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Before my mother died, she told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:28.94,Main,,0,0,0,,"The Fish-Men suffer discrimination,\Nso claim that you're a kappa."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:38.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Kawamatsu the Kappa.\NI've been living off leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:43.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you for saving me\Nand treating me to such a delicious meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:46.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:49.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Can I eat all of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:52.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll cook a new one, so wait for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:56.10,Main,,0,0,0,,No, that's not necessary. It's still edible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:16:02.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I behaved rudely.\NI wasted food.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:04.86,Main,,0,0,0,,You've grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry-meow, Kappa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll eat it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:13.99,Main,,0,0,0,,It's still too hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:18.04,Main,,0,0,0,,What a funny cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:23.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Neko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:27.90,Main,,0,0,0,,There are still creatures\NI've never seen out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:32.67,Main,,0,0,0,,By seeing you guys,\NI can't wait to set sail again one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:33.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:35.30,Main,,0,0,0,,This world is a big place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:37.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay. Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:41.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean... Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:46.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Let us stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:48.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Were you listening to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:50.40,Main,,0,0,0,,We have no place to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:53.40,Main,,0,0,0,,All right! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:57.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Yay! Yaaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:58.53,Main,,0,0,0,,We got more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:02.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess you can't reject anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:05.83,Main,,0,0,0,,That's fine, but we're in a bind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:10.56,Main,,0,0,0,,You lent money to Orochi without asking me again!\NHe's a scumbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.56,0:17:15.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, he's independent now,\Nbut he's still tied to Yasu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:16.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I must help him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:24.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Without noise, on tiptoe, stealthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:26.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay? Those are the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:28.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:30.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Don't be afraid of Yasuie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:34.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Without noise, on tiptoe, stealthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:37.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Without noise, on tiptoe, stealthy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:46.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Why did you try to steal this much money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:48.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden-san is out of money!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:52.09,Main,,0,0,0,,If you wanna kill us,\Njust do it, you hedgehog!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:55.41,Main,,0,0,0,,If it'll help Oden-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.41,0:17:58.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm happy to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:12.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Oden... he took such strange people in...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:17.15,Main,,0,0,0,,You can have the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:19.32,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:23.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Yasuie-sama! What about Hakumai's finances?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:24.66,Main,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:32.17,Main,,0,0,0,,You guys, use this money.\NI will give it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:36.42,Main,,0,0,0,,More money?! That can't be true!\NIs it a trap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:44.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you like Oden?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:52.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, use this money to fix yourselves up,\Nlearn good manners,...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:56.28,Main,,0,0,0,,...buy books, and get yourself educated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:18:59.61,Main,,0,0,0,,That doesn't sound like us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:07.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:09.82,Main,,0,0,0,,No! Speak from your stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:11.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:23.64,Main,,0,0,0,,With hoodlums like you as retainers,\NOden will humiliate himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:28.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden-sama, will you please elaborate on\Nhow you feel today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:31.57,Main,,0,0,0,,This ganmodoki is exquisite!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:35.52,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you guys?!\NYou're so creepy these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:39.49,Main,,0,0,0,,He will become the Shogun of the Wano Country.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:45.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Those who support him ought to be\Nthe best samurai in the Wano Country!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:11.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course, you must protect your lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:15.81,Main,,0,0,0,,But someday, be the guardian angels of...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:19.36,Main,,0,0,0,,...the capital and the whole Wano Country!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:30.49,Main,,0,0,0,,The party of Kuri's Daimyo\Nwill come to the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:32.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't get robbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:35.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden-sama's vassals are ruffians.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:37.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Look! They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:40.17,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:12.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa! What happened to those samurai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:15.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Were Oden-sama's vassals always that cool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:17.67,Main,,0,0,0,,No, they've changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:21.05,Main,,0,0,0,,It's like the Shogun's procession!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:35.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The regal postures of those samurai were\Nso glorious that some people even forgot to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:42.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And one could have seen people's knees\Ngive way everywhere in the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:47.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:21:52.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden! You became such a great man!\NEveryone is surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:57.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I've only been made great.\NI haven't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:22:01.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I-I cannot believe\Nyou feel grateful to others!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:03.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be frightened!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.55,0:22:16.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hearing about his father's illness, Oden rushed to the capital and was relieved to see him fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:20.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,However, this was the last time\Nthey would talk to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:28.20,Main,,0,0,0,,People are living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:31.91,Translation Info,,0,0,0,,オヤジ Oyaji, Pops
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:31.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Oyaji, it'll take a week to repair it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:34.58,Main,,0,0,0,,The cargo is mostly water damaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.58,0:22:37.41,Main,,0,0,0,,We need to go get food and supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.41,0:22:39.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Who wants to go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.21,0:22:42.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Almost everyone\Nsince we all need some exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.79,0:22:44.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm coming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.71,0:22:47.64,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't. You're an apprentice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:51.30,Main,,0,0,0,,We climbed up the falls, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.14,0:22:55.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is there sea and an island here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:12.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Getting in fights and tossed about in raging waves\Ndoesn't deter Oden's ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:18.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He dreams of the unknown world,\Nand to make his way out, he'll tackle any hardship!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.57,0:23:25.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will Oden be able to win Whitebeard and his people's hearts and set out for an adventure with them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:27.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Next time on One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.37,0:23:30.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden's Determination! \NWhitebeard's Trials!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:32.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
